Show him the suitcase and let him pick it up , he said . 
If he makes a wrong movement , call me , and I'll shoot him . 
Titania pointed out the suitcase , which she had stowed at the back of her cupboard behind some clothes . 
The chef showed no insubordination , and the three returned downstairs . 
Very well , said Roger . 
We'll go down in the shop where we can see better . 
Perhaps he's got a first folio Shakespeare in here . 
