She put out her hand for the book . 
Stop ! cried Aubrey , and seized her arm . 
Don't touch that book ! Titania shrank back , frightened by his voice . 
Had everyone gone insane ? Here , Mr. Metzger , said Aubrey , you put that book back on the shelf where it belongs . 
Don't try to get away . 
I've got this revolver pointed at you . 
He and Roger were both startled by the chef's face . 
