He placed the case carefully on the floor , and picked the Cromwell volume out of it . 
Where would you want it to go ? he said in an odd voice . 
This is a valuable book . 
On the fifth shelf , said Roger . 
Over there For God's sake stand back , said Aubrey . 
There's something damnable about this . 
You poor fools ! cried Metzger harshly . 
